==Public schools==
The [[Carroll County Public Schools (Maryland)|Carroll County Public Schools]] School system is the ninth largest [[school district]] in the state of Maryland.

==Miscellaneous==
*The newspaper of record is the ''[[Carroll County Times]]''.
*The county was used for scenes in the [[Tim Allen]] movie ''[[For Richer or Poorer]]'' and the [[Richard Gere]] and [[Julia Roberts]] movie ''[[Runaway Bride (1999 film)|Runaway Bride]]''.

[[Chris Rock]] stood in front of North Carroll Middle School during his speech in the movie "Head of State."

